on thirds
Homonym Number:
Word Class:phrase
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a sheep-grazing arrangement where a grazier is allotted a proportion of the wool and offspring of the flock.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: rural, usually sheep farming; occas thirds
